          "Who You Know",
          "Your relationship to these people is described. This may mean they do not know you."
        ],
        [
          "Marcus Jonak (Toreador) (Michael Steinbach)",
          "A Toreador actor, you recognize him from your time in the old court. You're not sure what's happened during the the time you slept - perhaps he can help fill you in."
        ],
        [
          "Franklin Richards (Tremere) (Joe Butts)",
          "Another Kindred you recognize, this time from the chantry itself. You don't think Richards knows what you did, but it's in your best interest to keep him pleased with you so that even if your secret does come out, he will help cover for you."
        ],
        [
          "Lupo Salamanca (Brujah) (Brodie Aberson)",
          "You were ghouls together, now you're both vampires! You wonder if he still remembers you."
        ],
        [],
        [
          "Starting Goals",
          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "If you have learned anything during your time as a Tremere, it's that no sin is truly unforgivable if the penance is service to the clan. In anticipation of your secret getting out, build up your reputation within the clan. Help rediscover a lost Thaumaturgy path, collect rare occult books, contribute significantly to the chantry... anything you can use to defend yourself on charges of disloyalty to the clan."
        ],
        [
          "And if the straight and narrow path doesn't work out, there's always blackmail. See what you can do about collecting dirt on your fellow Tremere in case you need to take the low road."
        ],
        [
          "Rebuild your mortal contacts, and regain control of the Los Angeles library system, which is even grander and more beautiful than when you went into torpor."
        ],
